{"title":"Silmakreem","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"organic-eye-cream-15ml","title":"Vielö Organic Eye Cream 15ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNourishing organic eye cream to deliver long-lasting hydration and effectively nurture the delicate skin around the eyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), organic rosehip seed oil (soothing), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic sunflower oil (nurturing) and organic extracts of camomile (invigorating), eyebright (strengthening) and mallow (protecting).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Apply to clean and dry skin. Massage in gently. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Rosa Canina Fruit Oil**, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate\/ Stearate*, Glycerin**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Cetyl Alcohol*, Aqua*, Prunus Armeniaca Kernel Oil**, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil**, Sodium Levulinate*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Xanthan Gum*, Sodium Anisate, Tocopherol*, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid*, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Matricaria Chamomilla Flower Extract**, Malva Sylvestris Leaf Extract**, Euphrasia Officinalis Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Limonene**\/***, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Citral**\/***.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e* from natural origin (99,7%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e** certified organic (87,1%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49093397217607,"sku":null,"price":47.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-eye-cream-15ml-750536.jpg?v=1739897336"},{"product_id":"madara-anti-fatigue-eye-rescue-cream-15ml","title":"MÁDARA Anti-Fatigue Eye Rescue Cream 15ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThe unique multi-layered texture firms and smooths away signs of fatigue. Age-defying Smart Antioxidant complex of Lichen, Moss, Fern and Alchemilla hydrates and corrects fine lines and wrinkles.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSkin-dynamising natural aescin boosts circulation and strengthens capillaries to depuff and reduce dark circles and brighten up the eye area.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply 4 small drops around the eye and pat into the skin. Use morning and night.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Cetearyl Alcohol, Isoamyl Laurate, Arachidyl Alcohol, Behenyl Alcohol, Dipalmitoyl hydroxyproline, Sodium levulinate, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Arachidyl Glucoside, Caffeine, Propanediol, Aroma, Glyceryl Caprylate, Sodium anisate, CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), Mica (CI 77019), Xanthan Gum, Aesculus Hippocastanum (Horse Chestnut) Seed Extract, Alchemilla Vulgaris (Lady's Mantle) Extract, Calendula Officinalis (Calendula) Flower Extract, Chamomilla Recutita (Camomile) Flower Extract, Coco-glucoside, Sodium PCA, Xylitylglucoside, Anhydroxylitol, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Polypodium Vulgare (Fern) Rhizome Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Sodium phytate, Tocopherol, Xylitol, Potassium Hydroxide, Cetraria Islandica (Lichen) Thallus Extract, Citric acid, Sphagnum Magellanicum (Moss) Extract, Vanillin, Escin, Benzyl Salicylate, Limonene, Citral, Linalool, Eugenol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49887831753031,"sku":null,"price":32.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-anti-fatigue-eye-rescue-cream-15ml-826053.jpg?v=1739897249"},{"product_id":"hoia-super-firming-eye-serum-instant-effect-10ml","title":"HOIA Super Firming Eye Serum Instant Effect 10ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEye Serum is supercharged with innovative active ingredients such as botanical vitamin A and C, botox-like peptides, caffeine, niacinamide, hyaluronic acid, rosehip oil, botanical retinol bakuchiol, all infused into organic peppermint and rosemary plant waters, which are grown and distilled in Saaremaa. This rich cocktail instantly cools, soothes and smooths the under-eye area, fine lines, reduces dark circles and keeps the eye area bright, moisturized and beautiful. Lightweight and fast-absorbing.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply small amount to eye area and massage until absorbed. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003e*Rosimarinus Officinalis Distillate, *Mentha Piperita Distillate, Sargassum Fluitans\/Natans Extract, *Rosa Canina Seed oil, Tetrapeptide-21, Nicotanamid, Caffeine, Bakuchiol, Ascorbyl Tetraisopalmitate, Sodium Hyaluronate, Hydrolized Sodium Hyaluronate, Tocopheryl-acetat, Hydroxypropyl Methylcellulose, Pullulan, Porphyridium Cruentum Extract, Butylene Glycol, Glyerin, Haematococcus Pluvialis extract, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Magnolia Officinalis Bark extract, Glyceryl Caprylate, Pentylene Glycol, Citric acid, Mica , CI77891, CI 77491, Lauroyl Lysine. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50324778025287,"sku":null,"price":38.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-super-firming-eye-serum-instant-effect-10ml-615777.png?v=1739897243"},{"product_id":"hej-organic-sensitive-eye-cream-serum-15ml","title":"HEJ Organic Sensitive Eye Cream-Serum 15ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSensitive Eye Cream-Serum's delicate texture melts with the warmth of your skin. Squalane reduces moisture loss, combats dryness wrinkles and gives the skin a silky feel. It supports the decongestant and calming effects of paracress and safflower oil.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSilky care for the eye area ensures an alert look\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eParacress reduces fine lines and redness\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSqualane retains moisture around the eyes\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEspecially for sensitive skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAllergen-reduced perfume oil, 100% vegan and natural\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eDistribute one pump onto your fingertips. Gently tap on the area under your eyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Glycerin, Squalane, Coco-Caprylate, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate\/ Stearate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cannabis Sativa Seed Oil*, Carthamus Tinctorius Seed Oil, Oleic Acid, Sodium Levulinate, Hypericum Perforatum Extract*, Avena Sativa Kernel Extract*, Chamomilla Recutita Flower Extract*, Triethyl Citrate, Terminalia Arjuna Bark Extract, Xanthan Gum, Tocopherol, Spilanthes Acmella Flower\/Leaf\/Stem Extract, Astragalus Membranaceus Root Extract, Lecithin, Uniquinone Ubiquinone, Citric Acid, Sodium Anisate \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*ingredients from certified organic agriculture\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50905787072839,"sku":null,"price":13.1,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-sensitive-eye-cream-serum-15ml-872495.png?v=1739897181"},{"product_id":"berrichi-age-defence-eye-cream-15ml","title":"BERRICHI Age Defence Eye Cream 15ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eBrightening eye cream for aging skin with powerful natural ingredients and science based formula.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLightly absorbable eye cream deeply moisturizes and nourishes the delicate skin around the eyes. The cream prevents and relieves signs of aging, reduces dark circles under the eyes and restores the skin’s natural function and protective barriers.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEye eye cream contains powerful antioxidants furcellaran and astaxanthin, which have anti-aging and deep moisturising effects has been confirmed in many scientific studies. We get furcellaran from algae grown in Estonian waters, astaxanthin from other clean and Nordic sea plants.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eConcerns about dark circles under the eyes and pigmentation are alleviated by koji-acid and alpha arbutin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMoisturizes and nourishes delicate skin around the eyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSilky and soft texture.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEasily absorbed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrevents and reduces signs of aging.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eReduces dark circles under the eyes and pigment spots.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eContains furcellaran,\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eastaxanthin, aloe vera,\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003cspan\u003ecacay\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eoil, apricot oil, avocado oil,\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekoji acid and alpha arbutin.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor all skin types and for ages 25+\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a small amount of cream around the clean eye area with your finger, pat gently and evenly onto the skin. \u003cspan\u003eYou will notice improvements in 2 weeks of use.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado Oil)*, Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil)*, Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate (Olivem1000), Cetearyl Alcohol, Simmondsia Chinesis seed oil (Organic Jojoba oil)*, Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay Oil), Glycerin**, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice\/Potassium Sorbate\/Sodium Benzoate\/Citric acid (Aloe Vera), Dehydroacetic Acid\/Benzoic Acid\/Benzyl Alcohol\/Sorbic Acid (Sharomix705), Koji acid, A-arbutin, Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haemotococcus pluvialis\/Tocopherol (Astaxanthin oil)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**Made using organic ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e98,9% natural origin of total\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51062111764807,"sku":null,"price":27.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-age-defence-eye-cream-15ml-587219.png?v=1739897155"},{"product_id":"upcircle-beauty-eye-cream-with-cucumber-hyaluronic-acid-coffee-15ml","title":"UpCircle Beauty Eye Cream with Cucumber, Hyaluronic Acid + Coffee, 15ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eA gentle dermatologically approved eye cream with hyaluronic acid and coffee to brighten, refresh and renew, reducing the appearance of dark circles and fine lines.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis multi-award winner is suitable for all skin types. Use both morning and night. The eye cream should be the first part of the moisturising section of your skincare routine. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspiring, upcycling, uplifting: This brightening eye cream for dark circles is made with coffee oil extracted from repurposed grounds and anti-inflammatory maple bark extract, a by-product of the wood industry.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a small amount around the contour of your eye. Use morning and night.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Glycerin, C14-22 Alcohols, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil*, Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil, Cucumis Sativus (Cucumber) Fruit Extract*, Xanthan Gum, Coffea Arabica (Coffee) Seed Extract, Acer Rubrum (Maple) Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Calendula Officinalis Extract*, Rosmarinus Officinalis (Rosemary) Leaf Extract*, Anthemis Nobilis (Chamomile) Flower Oil, Tocopherol, Sodium Hydroxide, C12-20 Alkyl Glucoside, Potassium Sorbate, Sorbic Acid, Citric Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Salicylic Acid, Benzyl Alcohol, Limonene**. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organically grown ingredients \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**Natural constituent of essential oils listed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e99% NATURAL INGREDIENTS\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHandmade | Social Good | Recycled Materials | Zero Waste | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources | Non Toxic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"UpCircle Beauty","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51132960080199,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/upcircle-beauty-eye-cream-with-cucumber-hyaluronic-acid-coffee-15ml-835499.png?v=1740808675"}],"url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/silmakreem.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}